ier man gjerne at \u00absola snur\u00bb p\u00e5 dette tidspunktet. For \u00e5 ikke skape noen misforst\u00e5elser, sola g\u00e5r fortsatt fra \u00f8st til vest.", "I gamle tider ble det gjerne sagt at man ikke skulle gj\u00f8re noe arbeid som krever at noe g\u00e5r rundt. Man sa ogs\u00e5 at regn f\u00f8r sommersolverv ga t\u00f8rrv\u00e6r etter, og omvendt."]}, {"field": "category0", "value": "vaeret"}, {"field": "contenthash", "value": "04937ec68c8ea7297ce3bd205088685c640f0ab58ede913dd51ba9a7739df501"}, {"field": "createtime", "value": "2016-02-06T12:44:16.000Z"}, {"field": "description", "value": "Tr\u00f8nderne har ikke sett mye til den, men i dag \u00absnur\u00bb sola."}, {"field": "dominantimage", "value": "http://www.adressa.no/incoming/article1358728.ece5/ALTERNATES/w980-default/SelbuFlom03"}, {"field": "dominantimagedimensions", "value": "980x551"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnail", "value": "http://content-thumbnail.cxpublic.com/content/dominantthumbnail/37c7ebc224b85eb73024542f03ffcda37c564df2.jpg?5936ce0a"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnaildimensions", "value": "300x169"}, {"field": "heading", "value": ["\u00c5rets lyseste d\u00f8gn -adressa.no", "Optimister blir ikke v\u00e6rsyke", "- Bruk v\u00e6ret", "Ikke alvorlig syk", "- Ingen grunn til pessisme", "Glemmer problemer", "G\u00e5 ut av huset", "Sola \u00absnur\u00bb i dag"]}, {"field": "id", "value": "37c7ebc224b85eb73024542f03ffcda37c564df2"}, {"field": "keyword", "value": ["v\u00e6ret", "nedb\u00f8r", "storm", "nina", "ivar", "hilde", "frida", "orkan"]}, {"field": "keywords", "value": "v\u00e6ret,nedb\u00f8r,storm,nina,ivar,hilde,frida,orkan"}, {"field": "kw-category", "value": "vaeret"}, {"field": "kw-concept", "value": ["\u00e5rets lyseste", "\u00e5rets lyseste d\u00f8gn", "v\u00e6r"]}, {"field": "kw-entity", "value": ["ringve", "sponhuset", "wikipedia"]}, {"field": "kw-location", "value": ["stavanger", "tr\u00f8ndelag", "trondheim", "bergen"]}, {"field": "kw-pageclass", "value": "article"}, {"field": "k